00:28:06.811 --> 00:28:12.719
I saw him rise up and I saw a liberation coming to the Cuban people.

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:19.960
I saw our military, certain units with crosses that were symbolic to this.

00:28:19.961 --> 00:28:29.798
Now, I'm not going all into this for a reason. There's a lot of you who will never make it to the end of this video.

00:28:29.799 --> 00:28:35.799
I'm not trying to be snide; I'm saying there was a reason why the Lord waited until many of you left.

00:28:35.800 --> 00:28:52.411
But I try to give you what I feel in my spirit, too. If you want to pray with it, pray. I saw these hands.

00:28:52.412 --> 00:29:26.459
I saw that the guy who was over it had chemical warfare weapons for viruses that, when people got them, they got these big sores on their bodies that looked like fire ant bites, round like a half dollar.

00:29:26.460 --> 00:29:40.199
Some were sores and boils all over the body, full of white infection with a black center.

00:29:40.200 --> 00:30:00.439
It was nasty. I don't know if this was smallpox. But I saw a canister that looked like a cylinder with a biohazard symbol on the side.

00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:11.236
As I was praying, I heard 'burros'. Burro—Braden said 'burro'means donkey.

00:30:11.237 --> 00:30:16.623
As we were praying in Spanish, the Lord showed us about mules in the night.

00:30:16.624 --> 00:30:34.479
I saw the American Coast Guard with radar on the tip of their boat, spinning around, able to detect if there was trouble in the water coming towards America.

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:48.257
I saw the United States Coast Guard heavily patrolling Florida, and they were not able to penetrate the patrol like they were when Joe Biden was here.

00:30:48.258 --> 00:30:58.123
Thank God for President Trump. I saw these patrol boats really doing their jobs.

00:30:58.124 --> 00:31:13.039
