00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:35.078
Now, if I'm wrong, I'm wrong. But that's what I saw. Now, you say, 'Well, Brandon, they do.'I saw that they didn't.

00:31:35.079 --> 00:31:47.878
If they do, then I missed it. But I'm telling you what I saw in the vision.

00:31:47.879 --> 00:31:57.003
I saw our heroes—our men and women that protect our nation. God bless them.

00:31:57.004 --> 00:32:14.839
The Lord said, 'Pray for them.'That's all I will say. And I saw cyberattacks coming to Cuba in the darkness again.

00:32:14.840 --> 00:32:44.895
I saw a liberation and the Lord said, 'Do this by surprise and keep your mouth shut, leadership, for don't underestimate your enemy.'Announcing things and too much chatter is not healthy for the people going in, the ones risking their lives as you sit behind a desk pushing a button.

00:32:44.896 --> 00:32:54.891
Be still. Pray for them. I saw the chatter in the still of the night, like in Venezuela. The Lord said, 'Watch this.

00:32:54.892 --> 00:33:05.439
Pray for them.'But out of retaliation, that which was in the mountain was used upon the land.

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:17.003
The guy in Cuba is nuts—the leader. I saw a mountain glow with a ripple of a wave that looked like an atom bomb.

00:33:17.004 --> 00:33:28.578
It went straight up and off the side of a mountain in retaliation to him losing his position.

00:33:28.579 --> 00:33:42.629
I thought, surely he wouldn't do that to his own people. But it was on the side of a mountain, looking like a mushroom cloud.

00:33:42.630 --> 00:34:01.119
I saw Fidel Castro's face and his beard. The Lord said he got this weapon back when he was in power and he's had it the whole time.

00:34:01.120 --> 00:34:34.519
It was a trade with Russia—I don't know what they traded, maybe oil. It was during the Cold War. I heard 'KGB'.

00:34:34.520 --> 00:34:50.273
So that's a little rundown for those who don't want to pray with us, so you can keep up and maybe help pray.

00:34:50.274 --> 00:34:55.199
I can present it to you, and if you don't want to pray, don't. But I pray you do.

00:34:55.200 --> 00:34:59.728
Pray for Cuba, pray for our president, pray for them to make great decisions.

00:34:59.729 --> 00:35:21.836
We must take no counsel from the ungodly as we pray for Cuba and Iran, that this ends quickly and they get all the plutonium.

00:35:21.837 --> 00:35:38.773
Uranium. Thank you. We're not in Back to the Future. It's what the Russians are after. All of it is coming to a head, folks.

00:35:38.774 --> 00:35:48.119
I truly believe we're about to see some amazing things with the church, but as we see these things, it's going to get darker in the world.

00:35:48.120 --> 00:35:53.738
We're getting closer and closer to the Lord's return, and I'm excited to be a part of it.

00:35:53.739 --> 00:36:03.561
Are you? So let's pray. Was that a good highlight? Did I get enough?

