Ow, my elbow just popped. Did you hear that? Wow, that was loud.

00:36:29.863 --> 00:36:38.532
Goodness gracious. Thank you, Lord, I'm healed. Thank you, Father.

00:36:38.533 --> 00:36:45.713
My knees, my body... Thank you, Lord. I'm getting this weight off. Obesity is terrible on your joints.

00:36:45.714 --> 00:36:58.382
